<br>
Add another 400hp dmg absorption from diamond skin.<br>
<br>
Add the 1000 pvp dmg ht at 60 that is now a lifetap once you've purchased the apropriate AA skill.<br>
<br>
Add a 220 pvp dmg tap in 2.5 seconds once every 2 minutes.<br>
<br>
Add 270 pvp dmg taps every 6.1 seconds (taps are only pvp reduced to 80%)<br>
<br>
What you have is a hybrid class that can over the course of  roughly 36 seconds absorb 5570 points of dmg while dishing out 2570 points of dmg without ever turning on auto attack.<br>
<br>
